{"tid":190044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人耳水不平衡？","createTime":"2017-04-07T01:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T03:27:36.000Z","uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b478e93f5373f67f3579094d43954828a54f0a8b","tid":190044,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:01:20.000Z","msg":"唔知應該開邊個台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟今朝6點幾醒果時係打則訓<br />\n一轉邊訓就突然好暈 同埋好想噁<br />\n<br />\n咁果陣諗住訓下無事<br />\n<br />\n點知口岩口岩起身個情況都係無改善...<br />\n<br />\n上網睇我嘅症狀就係耳水不平衡<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有相同狀況啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ddba47a78819028b9d7a0d526c88c0c46c4e50","tid":190044,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我維持左10年左右<br />\n醫生話冇得斷尾<br />\n身子弱果排就會天旋地轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0f2df552eeded2e519f46ee88e6b0a814d6e1b","tid":190044,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我維持左10年左右<br />\n醫生話冇得斷尾<br />\n身子弱果排就會天旋地轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5002fced54ba80a3acf91ffe7bab3ba7454a5d","tid":190044,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T01:06:55.000Z","msg":"點解會無