<br />\n<br />\n我諗感覺差唔多<br />\n要即刻訓係度<br />\n次次都暈足幾日先慢慢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af3b095ab59e64f37c990b4e5c765c180e238b28","tid":190044,"uid":84154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"狂嘔  睇完醫生過一日好番"},{"pid":"828be1af52ac45f2598c5d502151186ef4b92c79","tid":190044,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試過<br />\n好撚恐怖<br />\n上下左右都分唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係天旋地轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗感覺差唔多<br />\n要即刻訓係度<br />\n次次都暈足幾日先慢慢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今朝係向左打則訓無事<br />\n轉向右邊就黎料"},{"pid":"53c4a376aeaca887f328846d7910c3818c5ab17e","tid":190044,"uid":57100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"如果病發 最好訓床休息 唔好轉位置 最緊要多d休息 注意返水份補充"},{"pid":"1e9a99e6884ae788cdd8b41c9ee8b9dbddc98a18","tid":190044,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T03:27:36.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}